{"tid":279551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"住劏房戶四口家節衣縮食 月月清袋","createTime":"2017-06-11T11:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T16:53:42.000Z","uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5483baeda1174338789d5e6477d541d6062d469d","tid":279551,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:12:57.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】一家四口居於深水埗唐樓不足200呎劏房的袁小姐，申領公屋逾4年未有消息。她的兒子成績雖較落後，卻無法負擔補習費用，「是不公平，但其他人有錢，我們沒錢，也沒有辦法」。 <br />\n<br />\n袁小姐育有4歲兒子及7個月大女兒，在髮型屋工作的丈夫月入1.2萬元，另要申領低收入在職家庭津貼，半年有約1萬元。她稱每月租金和水電煤氣已花掉一半收入，加上奶粉尿片花費和各項生活開支，每月皆「清袋」，「有時有數百元剩下，但下個月小孩又生病，又用光了」。<br />\n<br />\n袁小姐帶小孩出外也是在深水埗區內，甚少遠遊。她與丈夫一天只吃一斤菜、手心大的豬肉，節衣縮食過生活。<br />\n<br />\n- See more at: <a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170610/s00001/1497030854226#sthash.Zy3LzLJZ.dpuf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170610%2Fs00001%2F1497030854226%23sthash.Zy3LzLJZ.dpuf&d=X%2BSTMYEMSAHrUNu%2FG3a63%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=b3b1050d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170610%2Fs00001%2F1497030854226%23sthash.Zy3LzLJZ.dpuf&h=f4f66d1a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170610/s00001/1497030854226#sthash.Zy3LzLJZ.dpuf</a>"},{"pid":"f4a0c44dcf36764a3df3f5272f071af4837ce729","tid":279551,"uid":79471,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T11:14:38.000Z","msg":"點解要生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc814515e40eb22ccfc73aae36f5dc7e1913370f","tid":279551,"uid":4574,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T12:18:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解要生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n等你同我養"},{"pid":"350ce36c760b89ab2d5fc875177cab7d9026018b","tid":279551,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T12